# WMS Test Suite Documentation

## Overview

This directory contains all tests for the Warehouse Management System (WMS). The test suite is organized to provide comprehensive coverage including unit tests, integration tests, end-to-end (E2E) tests, and performance tests.

## Test Structure

```
tests/
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ unit/                    # Unit tests for components and utilities
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ integration/             # API and service integration tests  
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ e2e/                     # End-to-end browser tests with Playwright
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ performance/             # Performance and load tests
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ build/                   # Build verification scripts
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ vulnerability-tests/     # Security and edge case tests
‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ __tests__/              # Legacy test structure (being migrated)
```

## Running Tests

### All Tests
```bash
npm run test:all              # Run all test suites
npm run test:ci              # Run tests in CI mode with coverage
```

### Unit Tests
```bash
npm test                     # Run all unit tests
npm run test:unit           # Run only unit/ folder tests
npm run test:watch          # Run tests in watch mode
npm run test:coverage       # Run with coverage report
```

### Integration Tests
```bash
npm run test:integration    # Run integration tests
```

### E2E Tests
